WEBVTT

00:00.934 --> 00:02.265
<i>Previously on</i> One Tree Hill:

00:02.335 --> 00:05.566
-I want to move in with Dan.
-Over my dead body.

00:05.638 --> 00:06.969
What does Dan have over you?

00:07.040 --> 00:09.235
How did you convince her
that you didn't have HCM?

00:09.309 --> 00:12.005
I used Keith's negative-results letter.

00:12.078 --> 00:14.808
<i>She left to be with Chris.</i>
<i>She kissed him before she left.</i>

00:14.881 --> 00:17.349
My investigator found
something interesting about Dan.

00:17.417 --> 00:20.409
Let's just go slow, okay?

00:22.022 --> 00:23.080
Okay.

00:23.156 --> 00:25.181
You know there's a girl
you have feelings for.

00:25.258 --> 00:27.954
-Nathan--
-Look me in the eye. Tell me I'm wrong.

00:29.329 --> 00:31.263
You need to talk to her, Luke.

00:31.631 --> 00:35.032
-I've decided to tell Keith the truth.
-Maybe you won't have to.

00:35.101 --> 00:37.569
I think I'll just let this one go.

00:38.872 --> 00:40.897
Keith doesn't ever have to know.

